{
  "stem": "747.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so they wanted to grab some.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One day, one day, almost break might back because I was-- I resistant-- I am-- was resisting to let them have it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she got so angry, they gave her a dish into my spine, almost break it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So food was very scarce, very little, and very bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, to go to the toilet facilities, we could go twice a day with, with a-- somebody was-- with a guard who was taking us to the washroom.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the water was not permissible to drink, because it was poison in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all red.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, if you drink it, you will die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people didn't care and drunk it, and they got the diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At nighttime, we couldn't get out from the-- from the block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a wheelbarrow as a toilet in front of the building, if somebody really had to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But otherwise, it was strictly forbidden to, to leave the, the, the barrack where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a thousand women together, miserable, and fighting, and arguing, and smelly, and there was no ventilation, and hungry, and everybody was just plain miserable.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then finally, at three-- after the three weeks was over, I-- first, they-- they picked me to go to a place where it was a big dairy farming in [?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Budin ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Budin ?] or [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Budee ?]?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Budin. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Budin. ?] It was close by the farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was-- they just took the blood from my ear to testing for TB.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to wait a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
